dcterms:description: A dataset composed of in vivo mouse brain microvasculature data acquired using a photoacoustic microscopy system, containing 292 maximum-amplitude-projection images of mouse brain vasculature, all acquired at a wavelength of 532 nm.
dcterms:title: Mouse Brain Microvasculature Dataset

dcterms:description: Fully-sampled PAM images used as ground truth for training and testing deep learning models.
dcterms:title: Fully-Sampled PAM Images

dcterms:description: In vivo mouse brain imaging data described as part of the methodology without a specific reference.
dcterms:title: In Vivo Mouse Brain Imaging Data
